summary: what’s really fun about the spider sense is that its like, without a doubt a mystical power but no one realizes it. Like, peter...
body: what’s really fun about the spider sense is that its like, without a doubt a mystical power but no one realizes it. Like, peter can sense danger, but he doesn’t always know what danger but in one timeline peter has a daughter that can sense the multiverse web with her spiderverse, and in another gwen marries miles and has a daughter that can literally predict the future. So like, Miles and Gwen go their whole lives thinking the spider bite just gave them a heightened awareness and then they have their first kid who one day walks up to them and very spookily says her spider sense told her that they’re going to stop a bank robbery today and they’re just going to have to be like “could we have been doing that this whole time?”
